Spanair in Talks With Turkish Over Investment, Expansion Reports

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-05-31T05:50:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/spanair-in-talks-with-turkish-over-investment-expansion-reports.html
Spanair SA is in talks with  Turk Hava
Yollari (THYAO)  AO, the company known as  Turkish Airlines , about
allowing the Turkish carrier to buy a stake of as much as 49
percent in the company, Expansion reported.  Conversations between the two parties are “very advanced,”
the newspaper said, citing people familiar with the talks it
didn’t identify by name.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
